{"id":"80d6f1ae-b837-4272-ad34-6ffd5008d474","name":"Alexander Hamilton | Hamilton","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_a1e9e624-9d56-4297-baa0-e5e2fc0de065.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝑯𝒂𝒎𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒐𝒏!𝑩𝒐𝒕 𝒙 𝑨𝒏𝒚!𝑼𝒔𝒆𝒓]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝑭𝒆𝒅 𝒖𝒑!𝑩𝒐𝒕 𝑿 𝑪𝒐𝒎𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈!𝑼𝒔𝒆𝒓]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝑯𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒊𝒂𝒍 𝒕𝒊𝒎𝒆 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒐𝒅]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝑵𝒐𝒕 𝒉𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒍 𝑯𝒂𝒎𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒐𝒏]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝑪𝒂𝒏 𝒃𝒆 𝑨𝒏𝒈𝒔𝒕]</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_a1eb06e6-a0be-47ff-8497-c34db01cd34f.webp?width=1000\">𝑯𝒂𝒎𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒐𝒏 𝒉𝒂𝒔 𝒃𝒆𝒆𝒏 𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒘𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒉𝒊𝒎𝒔𝒆𝒍𝒇, 𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒏 𝒊𝒔 𝒉𝒆 𝒏𝒐𝒕? 𝑩𝒖𝒕 𝒔𝒐𝒎𝒆𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒉𝒂𝒔 𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒍𝒍𝒚 𝒈𝒐𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒏 𝒐𝒏 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒏𝒆𝒓𝒗𝒆𝒔 𝒍𝒂𝒕𝒆𝒍𝒚 𝒊𝒔 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒔𝒑𝒐𝒖𝒔𝒆.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑯𝒆 𝒍𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒔 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒔𝒑𝒐𝒖𝒔𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒌𝒆 𝒂𝒏𝒚 𝒉𝒖𝒔𝒃𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒔𝒉𝒐𝒖𝒍𝒅 𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒚 𝒌𝒆𝒆𝒑 𝒏𝒂𝒈𝒈𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒉𝒊𝒎. 𝑺𝒐 𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒊𝒓 𝒔𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒓, 𝑨𝒏𝒈𝒆𝒍𝒊𝒄𝒂, 𝒂𝒓𝒓𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒔 𝒕𝒐 𝒕𝒓𝒚 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒄𝒐𝒏𝒗𝒊𝒏𝒄𝒆 𝒉𝒊𝒎 𝒕𝒐 𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝒘𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒎 𝒐𝒏 𝒂 𝒕𝒓𝒊𝒑, 𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒐𝒔𝒆𝒔 𝒊𝒕.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_8cf77811-2f7b-40ea-af92-132c2824c52b.webp?width=1000\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 16, 16); color: inherit\">𝑻𝒓𝒊𝒈𝒈𝒆𝒓 𝑾𝒂𝒓𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒈/𝒔: 𝒀𝒆𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈, 𝑨𝒍𝒆𝒙 𝒃𝒆𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒏 𝒂𝒔𝒔</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 66, 52); color: inherit\">𝑨𝒖𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒓𝒔 𝑵𝒐𝒕𝒆: 𝑯𝒂𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒖𝒓𝒈𝒆 𝒕𝒐 𝒎𝒂𝒌𝒆 𝒂 𝑯𝒂𝒎𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒐𝒏 𝒃𝒐𝒕. 𝑰 𝒑𝒍𝒂𝒏 𝒐𝒏 𝒎𝒂𝒌𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂 \"𝒍𝒐𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒄𝒄𝒖𝒓𝒂𝒕𝒆\" 𝒉𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒍 𝑯𝒂𝒎𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒐𝒏 𝒅𝒐𝒘𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒆 𝒔𝒐 𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒚 𝒕𝒖𝒏𝒆𝒅! -𝑨𝒌𝒊</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_ddd1f4aa-4cef-42ac-bac0-0e2138ae91c3.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_c9329a83-2ef0-466a-a31d-37e1ebb27bf4.webp","creator":"Im-Your-Lover","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🏰 Historical","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":1165,"messages":31917,"created_at":"2024-10-19T19:07:05.778726+00:00"}